General.Name: Alpha Group International plc
General.Description: Alpha Group International plc provides foreign exchange risk management and alternative banking solutions in the United Kingdom and internationally. The company offers forward currency contracts, option contracts, foreign exchange spot transactions, and payments collections and currency accounts services. It serves corporates and institutions. The company was formerly known as Alpha FX Group PLC and changed its name to Alpha Group International plc in December 2022. Alpha Group International plc was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.
